Package de.db.derpate.servlet

Enum ServletParameter

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ServletParameter>
      • de.db.derpate.servlet.ServletParameter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ServletParameter>
    public enum ServletParameter
extends java.lang.Enum<ServletParameter>
    This enum should unify the parameter names. It should be used by the frontend (as "name" for input fields <input name="ENUM" ...>) as well as the backend (BaseServlet).
    Author:
    MichelBlank
    See Also:
    BaseServlet
